---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="About - Simple Bytes"
    description="Simple Bytes is an independent product studio building focused tools and apps for domains, SEO, publishing, and everyday work."
>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>About Simple Bytes</h1>
        <p class="tagline">An independent product studio building focused software that respects your time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <section class="block">
            <h2>What we do</h2>
            <p>Simple Bytes builds and operates tools, apps, and platforms. Some we build from scratch, others we acquire and improve. Each one follows the same principle: do something useful without wasting your time.</p>
            <p>Our products span domains, SEO, publishing, icons, cooking, health, and productivity — wherever we see a clear problem and a way to solve it simply.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="block">
            <h2>How we work</h2>
            <p>We keep things small and focused. No venture funding, no growth-at-all-costs. We build products we want to use ourselves, ship them, and keep improving them. If a tool can be free, it is. If a product earns revenue, that funds the next one.</p>
            <p>We run everything ourselves — design, engineering, operations. That means we can move fast and make decisions based on what's right for the product, not what a board wants to hear.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="block">
            <h2>What we believe</h2>
            <ul class="values">
                <li><strong>Useful first.</strong> Every product starts with a real problem. If we wouldn't use it ourselves, we don't build it.</li>
                <li><strong>Simple by default.</strong> Fewer features, done well. Complexity is easy — simplicity takes work.</li>
                <li><strong>Respect people's time.</strong> No dark patterns, no unnecessary sign-ups, no friction for friction's sake.</li>
                <li><strong>Independent.</strong> Self-funded, self-directed. We answer to our users, not investors.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="block">
            <div class="cta-row">
                <a href="/projects" class="btn btn--primary">See our projects</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--secondary">Get in touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .hero {
        margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tagline {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 520px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 640px;
    }

    .block {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .block:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .block h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .block p {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .block p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .values {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.85rem;
    }

    .values li {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .values strong {
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>
